expandable.name: Asus MB511WS VivoBook
expandable.description:
Efficient Processor

Integrated with the Ryzen processor, the ASUS VivoBook 16X Laptop ensures smooth performance, even while performing demanding tasks. This processor is designed to enhance power efficiency and reduce heat generation, making it ideal for extended use. Moreover, you can expect quick load times, seamless multitasking, and effortless video editing with this processor.

expandable.name: Asus HX041W TUF A17
expandable.description:
TAKE ON ANY CHALLENGE

Always ready for action, the TUF Gaming A17 excels at gaming, streaming, and everything in between. Up to AMD Ryzen 4600-H Series CPU to fly through multitasking and more. Gameplay graphics are smooth with the latest GeForce GTX 1650 GPU which reliably delivers high frame rates for a ton of modern games. A superfast NVMe PCIe SSD speeds up load times, while an open SSD slot makes it easy to add terabytes more space for all your games.
